reviewText: not bad movie-its watchable but expected more-Eliska.

I was looking forward to watching "Paris Countdown" and was pleased to find that there is an English-language audio version on the DVD (the original French is there, too, along with English subtitles.) LOADS of action, suspense and a few scenes which are a bit difficult to watch, because of the graphic nature!

This is what happens when the bad guys meet the REALLY bad guys. Enjoy!
